## 1️⃣ CALENDAR SCREEN (Core da App)

### Objetivo
Mostrar TODAS as bills do mês visualmente. Um olhar e você sabe:
- Quanto deve pagar
- Quando vence
- O que já pagou
- Se está atrasado

### Design Principles

```
VISUAL HIERARCHY:
├─ Month/Year picker (top, but hidden when scrolling)
├─ Calendar grid (HUGE, 80% da screen)
│  ├─ Dates com:
│  │  ├─ Bills due (colored dots)
│  │  ├─ Amount ($1,800)
│  │  └─ Status (paid/unpaid/late)
│  └─ Today indicator (highlighted)
└─ Navigation (bottom bar)

COLOR CODING:
├─ 🔴 RED: Overdue (passed due date, unpaid)
├─ 🟡 YELLOW: Due soon (1-3 days, unpaid)
├─ 🟢 GREEN: On track (4+ days, unpaid)
├─ ⚪ GRAY: Paid (bill marked complete)
└─ 🔵 BLUE: Today (current date highlight)

INTERACTION:
├─ Tap on date → Shows bills for that day (modal/sheet)
├─ Swipe left/right → Previous/next month
├─ Pull to refresh → Sync with partner
├─ Long press → Quick actions (mark as paid, edit)
```

